== Ingredients ==
[[Category:Recipes]][[Category:Cake]]
* 1 cup brown sugar
* 1,5 cup flour
* 1 teaspoon baking powder
* 1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda (koeksoda)
* 1 teaspoon cinnamon
* 1 teaspoon koekkruiden / mixed spice
* 1 teaspoon vanilla essence
* 2 eggs
* Pinch of salt
* 100g chopped nuts (walnuts work well; roughly 3/4 of nuts in cake, other 1/4 on top of icing)
* 0,5 cup grated apple
* 0,5 cup grated carrot
* 0,75 cup oil

Topping:

* 1 thing of mascarpone
* enough icing sugar (100-200g?)

== Method ==

# Beat eggs, sugar and oil
# Add apple and carrot
# Mix all dry ingredients (minus walnuts)
# Beat 2 minutes with wooden spoon
# add walnuts
# Pour into greased tin
# Bake +/-20min at 190 degrees C (18/4/2013: took about 35 minutes in convection oven at 180)

